<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;h1&gt;Welcome to MINDNESS Quotes&lt;/h1&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;p&gt;Select a category for your quotes:&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;select id="quoteCategory"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;option value="inspirational"&gt;Inspirational&lt;/option&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;option value="motivational"&gt;Motivational&lt;/option&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;option value="funny"&gt;Funny&lt;/option&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/select&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;p&gt;Number of Images to Generate:&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;input type="number" id="numImages" value="5" min="1" max="20"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;button onclick="getQuotesAndImages()"&gt;Get Quotes and Images&lt;/button&gt;</p>
